text: Kirill Zinovich (; ; born 5 March 2003) is a Belarusian footballer. As of 2020, he plays for Minsk.Profile at pressball.by His brother Dzmitry Zinovich is also a professional footballer. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian footballers Category:Belarus youth international footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:FC Minsk players
